io.konik.zugferd.qualified

Class DateTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.konik.zugferd.qualified.DateTime

  • public class DateTime
extends Object

    Date Time

    Consist of the string date value and a code number. The code number indicates how to interpret the string date.

    See Also:
    UN/EDIFACT 2379 Date or time or period format code
